-- Threadneedle AM takes 2 percent stake in Fineco
-- By Lisa Jucca
-- Fri Jul 11, 2014 07:15AM EDT
-- None



MILAN, July 11 (Reuters) - UK-based Threadneedle Asset Management has bought a stake of 2.2 percent in Italian online bank Fineco <FBK.MI>, which listed on the Italian stock market earlier this month.

